1
00:00:08,330 --> 00:00:09,530
My name is Shen Luyi.

2
00:00:09,900 --> 00:00:11,730
My father was the Minister of Rites.

3
00:00:11,730 --> 00:00:13,960
He was thrown into the death row for treason,

4
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:16,260
and the whole family was reduced to slavery.

5
00:00:16,260 --> 00:00:19,300
You look good in this skin.

6
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:20,700
Change into this.

7
00:00:22,600 --> 00:00:24,300
My sworn enemy from childhood,

8
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:27,700
the second young miss of the Grand Tutor's family, Wei Yingying, bought my whole family

9
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:29,460
and sent me to her fiancé,

10
00:00:29,460 --> 00:00:31,060
the General Weibei's Manor,

11
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:32,460
to be a trial maid for her.

12
00:00:32,560 --> 00:00:35,330
I heard General Weibei comes from the grassroots.

13
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:36,560
He is a killing god.

14
00:00:36,760 --> 00:00:38,330
During your three-day trial,

15
00:00:38,330 --> 00:00:39,990
you must serve him carefully.

16
00:00:41,530 --> 00:00:43,200
Write down his length,

17
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,630
the duration,

18
00:00:44,630 --> 00:00:46,400
and his favorite ways.

19
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,260
Most importantly,

20
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:49,660
you little bitch,

21
00:00:49,830 --> 00:00:51,130
don't get any funny ideas

22
00:00:51,130 --> 00:00:52,160
about seducing the master.

23
00:00:52,160 --> 00:00:54,800
Otherwise, I'll go back and report to the Madam and the Second Young Miss,

24
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:58,300
and they will beat your sick old mother and your two younger siblings to death.

25
00:00:58,300 --> 00:00:59,060
Got it.

26
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:01,460
This is the strongest aphrodisiac.

27
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:02,900
But,

28
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:06,600
I heard when you were the First Young Miss of the Minister's Manor,

29
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:09,330
you were lovers with a strong, lowly stable boy.

30
00:01:09,330 --> 00:01:10,860
I guess you can do without this medicine.

31
00:01:10,860 --> 00:01:12,430
Grand Tutor Wei is a court official,

32
00:01:12,430 --> 00:01:14,300
always priding himself on propriety.

33
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:15,400
If the masters of the Wei Manor

34
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:17,600
knew the servants were so vulgar,

35
00:01:17,630 --> 00:01:18,700
they would punish you severely

36
00:01:18,700 --> 00:01:19,500
to set an example.

37
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:22,330
Still think you are the First Young Miss of the Minister's Manor?

38
00:01:22,330 --> 00:01:25,460
You are just a lowly trial maid now,

39
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:26,560
an object,

40
00:01:26,930 --> 00:01:28,500
not even a human.

41
00:01:28,630 --> 00:01:30,400
What are you so arrogant about?

42
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:35,860
Trading my useless innocence

43
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,660
for my family's survival,

44
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,400
it's worth it.

45
00:01:41,759 --> 00:01:43,200
It's just...

46
00:01:56,729 --> 00:01:57,560
General,

47
00:01:57,860 --> 00:02:00,230
the Grand Tutor's Manor sent a trial maid.

48
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,030
Throw her out.

49
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,160
I don't think that's a good idea.

50
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:07,000
Rumor has it in the capital that you have a blue face and fangs,

51
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,199
and are a killing god.

52
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,729
The Grand Tutor was just worried about his daughter

53
00:02:10,729 --> 00:02:12,300
so he sent a trial maid.

54
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:14,260
Trial my foot.

55
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:15,560
Then Grand Tutor Wei...

56
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,360
Who cares about Grand Tutor Wei?

57
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,730
I'll go to His Majesty tomorrow

58
00:02:18,730 --> 00:02:20,130
and call off the wedding.

59
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:23,000
General, you never get close to women,

60
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,530
nor do you accept the bestowed marriage.

61
00:02:24,530 --> 00:02:25,300
In your heart,

62
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:29,430
are you still thinking about the First Young Miss of the Minister's Manor?

63
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:42,260
I never had true feelings for you.

64
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:45,230
I just found you ridiculous

65
00:02:45,230 --> 00:02:46,630
and played with you.

66
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:50,760
How dare you try to kidnap me and elope?

67
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:52,300
I will beat you to death today

68
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:54,560
to protect my reputation.

69
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,930
I have been thinking about her.

70
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:06,930
I wish I could find her right now

71
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,960
and kill her with one strike.

72
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,560
Shen Luyi.

73
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,400
Lu Jingxing.

74
00:03:32,300 --> 00:03:33,100
Guards!

75
00:03:33,730 --> 00:03:35,000
Throw this maid out.

76
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:35,630
Tell the Grand Tutor's Manor,

77
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:36,090
get out.

78
00:03:38,730 --> 00:03:40,030
What's wrong, General?

79
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:40,760
Didn't you just say...

80
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,620
You get out too.

81
00:03:46,130 --> 00:03:47,530
If you look at her again,

82
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:49,360
I'll gouge your eyes out.

83
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,630
I won't look.

84
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:51,700
I'm leaving.

85
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:58,130
I haven't seen you in three years, Miss.

86
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,130
You're still as playful as ever.

87
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:03,760
Did you dress up as a test-marriage maid just for thrills?

88
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:07,060
Lu Jingxing, you really became a general.

89
00:04:08,130 --> 00:04:09,360
In just three years,

90
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,800
quelling the northwest rebellion,

91
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:13,560
the General Weibei with unparalleled military success

92
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,560
is actually Lu Jingxing.

93
00:04:18,029 --> 00:04:19,930
Looking at me now, Miss,

94
00:04:19,930 --> 00:04:21,700
are you filled with regret?

95
00:04:21,700 --> 00:04:23,760
You should have made sure I was dead

96
00:04:24,030 --> 00:04:26,760
before throwing me into the mass grave back then.

97
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:38,330
Don't worry, Miss.

98
00:04:38,330 --> 00:04:40,460
I've paid off those two servants handsomely.

99
00:04:40,460 --> 00:04:41,630
They know what to do.

100
00:04:41,630 --> 00:04:43,300
Lu Jingxing will definitely survive.

101
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:45,060
Go to my room right now,

102
00:04:45,060 --> 00:04:47,100
take out my pearl hair ornament,

103
00:04:47,300 --> 00:04:48,100
pawn it,

104
00:04:48,100 --> 00:04:49,700
and buy some wound medicine.

105
00:04:49,730 --> 00:04:51,130
While he's unconscious,

106
00:04:51,260 --> 00:04:52,430
apply the medicine secretly.

107
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:53,630
Don't let him notice.

108
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,730
He is now the Emperor's favored subject

109
00:04:56,730 --> 00:04:58,760
and in the same camp as Grand Tutor Wei.

110
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,930
Regarding what happened back then,

111
00:04:59,930 --> 00:05:01,830
I cannot reveal a single word to him.

112
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:03,260
It's just a twist of fate.

113
00:05:03,530 --> 00:05:05,060
Now I am the slave,

114
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,900
and you are the master, General.

115
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:08,560
Whatever the General wants,

116
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,930
he gets.
